<p><a id="TSJN-01-04-0055-kw-0001" class="keywordref" title="jump to Orders to Mr. Lamb in text" href="#TSJN-01-04-0055-ks-0001">Orders to Mr. Lamb</a>: Gates wrote this day to Commissary Lamb; a transcript of his letter, in a clerks hand but with corrections by TJ, is in <span class="ref-rep" title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ Library of Congress ]">DLC</span>.</p></div>
